类 DefaultHandlerResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apereo.cas.authentication.DefaultHandlerResult
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    java.io.Serializable, org.apereo.cas.authentication.HandlerResult

    public class DefaultHandlerResult
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.apereo.cas.authentication.HandlerResult
    Contains information about a successful authentication produced by an AuthenticationHandler. Handler results are naturally immutable since they contain sensitive information that should not be modified outside the AuthenticationHandler that produced it.
    从以下版本开始:
    4.0.0
